4 SYNOPSIS:
5 This bill would require app store providers to
6 verify the age of users, affiliate minor accounts with
7 parent accounts and obtain consent from the holder of
8 the parent account, notify users when an app makes a
9 significant change, give developers real-time access to
10 the age category and consent status for minor accounts,
11 and protect personal age verification data.
12 This bill would prevent app store providers and
13 developers from enforcing contracts against minors,
14 misrepresenting information in disclosures, and sharing
15 personal age verification data.
16 This bill would require developers to verify the
17 age of users, notify users of significant changes to
18 the app, and limit the use of age category data in
19 compliance with laws or regulations.
20 This bill would require the Attorney General to
21 adopt certain rules.
22 This bill would also authorize the Attorney
23 General to bring an action for a violation as a
24 deceptive trade practice.
